OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781394469
OL,3,CNorth East health trust told to make
OL,4,C'immediate improvements'
OL,6,FA North East health trust has been
OL,7,Ftold by the regulator that it must
OL,8,Fmake "immediate improvements" to the
OL,9,Fquality and safety of care it is
OL,10,Fproviding.
OL,12,FThe Care Quality Commission (CQC) has
OL,13,Fissued the instruction to County
OL,14,FDurham and Darlington NHS Foundation
OL,15,FTrust, following an inspection in
OL,16,FDecember 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
