CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781394469
OL,3,CNorth East health trust told to make
OL,4,C'immediate improvements'
OL,6,FCQC inspectors have downgraded their
OL,7,Frating of whether the trust is "well-
OL,8,Fled" from good to inadequate, and said
OL,9,Fthat during that inspection they found
OL,10,Fstandards of care had "deteriorated"
OL,11,Fsince their last visit.
OL,13,FThe regulator found the trust was in
OL,14,Fbreach of regulations relating to good
OL,15,Fmanagement and complaints, and issued
OL,16,Fthe trust with a warning notice.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781394469
OL,3,CNorth East health trust told to make
OL,4,C'immediate improvements'
OL,6,FMeanwhile, in a separate inspection at
OL,7,Fthe trust in October 2025 which looked
OL,8,Fat surgical services, the CQC found
OL,9,Fthat in this area, the trust "requires
OL,10,Fimprovement".
OL,12,FAmong the findings in their reports
OL,13,Fpublished on Friday (12 June), CQC
OL,14,Finspectors found:
OL,16,FChris Storton, CQC deputy director of
OL,17,Fhospitals in the north east, said: "We
OL,18,Fhave shared our findings with the
OL,19,FTrust's management, who are aware of
OL,20,Fthe improvements needed, including
OL,21,Faddressing the organisation's culture.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781394469
OL,3,CNorth East health trust told to make
OL,4,C'immediate improvements'
OL,6,F"We will continue to monitor the
OL,7,Ftrust, including through future
OL,8,Finspections, to ensure people remain
OL,9,Fsafe while improvements are made."
OL,11,FIn response to the CQC reports, County
OL,12,FDurham and Darlington NHS Foundation
OL,13,FTrust has told us that they have
OL,14,Fundertaken "significant work" to
OL,15,Fstrengthen patient safety, improve
OL,16,Fservices and support staff.
OL,18,FThe trust has also said that they
OL,19,Faccept the findings of the reports and
OL,20,Fthey remain fully committed to
OL,21,Fdelivering the improvements identified.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781394469
OL,3,CNorth East health trust told to make
OL,4,C'immediate improvements'
OL,6,FChief Executive Steve Russell said:
OL,7,F"We fully accept the findings of these
OL,8,Freports and apologise where we have
OL,9,Ffallen short of the standards our
OL,10,Fpatients, communities and colleagues
OL,11,Frightly expect.
OL,13,F"I know some of the findings in these
OL,14,Freports will be difficult to read and
OL,15,Fmay understandably cause concern. It
OL,16,Fis important that we are open and
OL,17,Fhonest about where improvements were
OL,18,Fneeded.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781394469
OL,3,CNorth East health trust told to make
OL,4,C'immediate improvements'
OL,6,F"It is also important to recognise
OL,7,Fthat these reports reflect a point in
OL,8,Ftime. Since the inspections took place
OL,9,Flate last year, a tremendous amount of
OL,10,Fwork has happened across the Trust to
OL,11,Fstrengthen patient safety, improve
OL,12,Fgovernance, support our staff and
OL,13,Fdrive improvement.
OL,15,F"We remain focused on delivering the
OL,16,Fimprovements identified, being open
OL,17,Fand transparent about our progress,
OL,18,Fand making sure those improvements are
OL,19,Ffelt by our patients, communities and
OL,20,Fcolleagues."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
